02:03:46.229 --> 02:03:47.941
I give you my word.

02:03:51.779 --> 02:03:53.153
George...

02:03:53.863 --> 02:03:56.492
...I've been working
on a plan called Cobra.

02:03:57.075 --> 02:03:58.744
I'd like your opinion.

02:03:58.951 --> 02:04:01.371
We've been slugging through
hedgerow country...

02:04:01.579 --> 02:04:04.749
...half an acre a day
and we've got to find a way out.

02:04:05.001 --> 02:04:06.544
I want to use this road.

02:04:06.752 --> 02:04:08.547
The Saint Lô-Periers road.

